{"id": "1388640397651218502", "channel_id": "1388640397651218502", "type": 0, "author_id": "197871477918269440", "author_name": "mac2492", "author_bot": false, "content": "The team lineup tutorial forces the player to select the first four Awakeners in their roster. If the player triggers the tutorial after rolling Awakeners from more than one realm then they cannot get past the tutorial. Screenshot is from <@1317096780835455003>. A few other users in the English community have experienced this issue as well.\n\nOne way this bug can occur is if the user bypasses the Argent Dawnlight banner at the start. I'm not sure about the exact conditions to reproduce this, but closing and opening the game at a certain point (I think before rolling?) did it for me.\n\nThe tutorial should either allow the user to select any four Awakeners or force the four story Awakeners to prevent this bug.", "timestamp": "2025-06-28T22:01:10.491000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1317096780835455003"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "please", "emoji_id": "1356053110375714817", "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1388640398070644811", "filename": "bug.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 77482, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388640397651218502/1388640398070644811/bug.jpg?ex=6a005766&is=69ff05e6&hm=fa4027fe66241f8db81fdf42bacd9d1f84ffd0617527a83c3a85f9cf4bb5fb81&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1388640397651218502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Tutorial can cause soft-lock if player has Awakeners from multiple realms.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
